# Shared FE kernel (portal)

File trong manifest **sync từ `nalee-sports-web`** — **không sửa trực tiếp** trên portal trừ transform `x-client-source: 'portal'`.

## Workflow

1. Sửa trên **web** (source of truth)
2. `node scripts/sync-shared-kernel.mjs` (workspace root)
3. `pnpm check:shared-sync` trong portal — phải pass trước merge

Manifest: [`scripts/shared-kernel-manifest.json`](../../../scripts/shared-kernel-manifest.json)  
ADR: [`docs/architecture/shared-fe-kernel-sync.md`](../../../docs/architecture/shared-fe-kernel-sync.md)

## App-local (KHÔNG sync)

- `lib/apollo/links.ts`, `client.ts`, `cache-type-policies.ts`
- `middleware.ts`, `lib/validation/schemas.ts`
